# ─── Local backups / scratch ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.bak
*.bak-*
# backup/ is Kev's own local nested copy of this tree (it has its own .git
# folder inside it). It was accidentally committed as a submodule gitlink with
# no .gitmodules entry (2026-07-XX, source commit unknown/pre-existing), which
# broke GitHub Pages' auto "pages build and deployment" workflow on every push
# ("fatal: No url found for submodule path 'backup' in .gitmodules", exit 128)
# -- fixed 2026-07-12 by untracking it (git rm --cached, local files untouched)
# and ignoring it here so it can never be re-added the same way.
backup/

